title: The Breakfast Club Lies (Jo Koy Interview and More)
itunes:title: The Breakfast Club Lies (Jo Koy Interview and More)
description:
Today on the show we had friend to the room comedian Jo Koy where he called out The Breakfast Club for their lies, his new special and new book and more. Also, Charlamagne gave another Floridan "Donkey of the Day" this time because a boss threatened to fire employees if Biden wins the election and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
